    "result": {"data":{"strapiPost":{"strapiId":3419,"title":"Starting Our Descent","topic":"Travel","slug":"starting-our-descent","coverImage":{"publicURL":"/static/c589929913c903168db232d026401137/89da0ec6d332f511be6271e93c262491.jpg"},"photoCredit":"Ern Low","date":"2021-08-03","content":"<p>Things are looking cheaper for travelers flying through XNA. </p><ul><li><strong>Sky-high savings: </strong>In 2019, the average round trip cost from XNA was about <a href=\"https://fareflightnwa.org/cost-of-flying-from-xna-drops-194-data-shows/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">$560</a>. Now, flights are <a href=\"https://fareflightnwa.org/cost-of-flying-from-xna-drops-194-data-shows/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">almost $200</a> less, due to <a href=\"https://fareflightnwa.org/cost-of-flying-from-xna-drops-194-data-shows/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">new flights and carriers</a> coming to the terminal.</li><li><strong>Double trouble: </strong>Carriers Allegiant and Frontier airlines have been <a href=\"https://fareflightnwa.org/cost-of-flying-from-xna-drops-194-data-shows/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">expanding at XNA</a>, and they've brought their <a href=\"https://fareflightnwa.org/cost-of-flying-from-xna-drops-194-data-shows/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">low-cost flights</a> with them. 17 of the 25 XNA flight destinations have seen fare <a href=\"https://fareflightnwa.org/fares-to-17-of-25-xna-destinations-decreased-fed-data-shows/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">decreases</a>.</li></ul><p>You can read more about the big savings <a href=\"https://fareflightnwa.org/cost-of-flying-from-xna-drops-194-data-shows/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a>.</p><p><em class=\"ql-size-small\">Story courtesy of Fare Flight NWA</em></p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"starting-our-descent"}},
